   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-1-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="NPC_Left_lewis.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-1-f" mid="267" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="192"><![CDATA[<html>$Headquarters Guard$<BR>Mr. President, a visitor has arrived.<BR>An envoy from the Edart Empire.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-1-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-1-g" mid="268" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="193"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>From the Empire? Without prior notice?<BR><BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(You hear the sound of footsteps climbing the Headquarters stairs.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-1-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2" mid="269" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="194"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Then I'll discourteously take my leave again today. Don't worry; I won't go far.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-" mid="316" select_type="5" />
      <talk_question mid="195"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>(What's happening so suddenly? I'll hide behind the curtain and watch.)<BR><BR></FONT><FONT color=#7e12d2>※ Hide in an appropriate location to see what happens.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2934_peep_point-2" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Enon.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2934_peep_point-2-a" mid="270" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="196"><![CDATA[<html>$Edart's Messenger Enon$<BR>Hello.<BR>Dear Merca President Vernicka.<BR>I am Enon, a messenger and follower of the Goddess from Edart Empire.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2934_peep_point-2-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Enon.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2934_peep_point-2-b" mid="271" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="197"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>Thank you for coming all this way.<BR>I'm afraid I haven't been able to organize a banquet since you arrived so suddenly. Please understand.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2934_peep_point-2-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Enon.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2934_peep_point-2-" mid="272" select_type="5" />
      <talk_question mid="198"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>As you know... many visitors have been sent secretly from the Empire to Merca in recent times.<BR>I reckoned you were one of them.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2934_peep_point-3" image="QN_Kali.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2934_peep_point-3-a" mid="273" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="199"><![CDATA[<html>$Kali$<BR>……<BR><BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Kali is hiding on the other side of the curtain listening in on the conversation between Vernicka and the Edart envoy.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2934_peep_point-3-a" image="QN_Kali.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2934_peep_point-3-b" mid="274" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="200"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>(Hey... it's that person from Lagendia.<BR>What's she trying to learn?)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2934_peep_point-3-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Enon.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2934_peep_point-3-c" mid="275" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="201"><![CDATA[<html>$Edart's Messenger Enon$<BR>I'm sure you know of the Empire's suspicions, Vernicka.<BR>We strongly suspect that you support a seditious group.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2934_peep_point-3-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Enon.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2934_peep_point-3-d" mid="276" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="202"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>Ha...<BR>Are you claiming Merca is in league with the Anti-Goddess Faction?<BR>The neutral country of Merca is willing to negotiate with anyone, whether they be humans or Childs.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2934_peep_point-3-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Enon.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2934_peep_point-3-e" mid="277" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="203"><![CDATA[<html>$Edart's Messenger Enon$<BR>I know.<BR>Merca's Heart is a neutral land where all may freely trade with each other.<BR>There is only one reason such a wonderful place can exist...</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2934_peep_point-3-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Enon.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2934_peep_point-3-f" mid="278" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="204"><![CDATA[<html>$Edart's Messenger Enon$<BR>And that is because the merciful Goddess Vestinel allows it to exist.<BR>You must therefore never forget<BR>that when the Goddess has lost her patience, that neutrality may be shattered.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2934_peep_point-3-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Enon.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2934_peep_point-3-g" mid="279" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>!!!!</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="205"><![CDATA[<html>$Edart's Messenger Enon$<BR>
In the name of the Goddess.<BR>I declare that Merca's Heart shall no longer be a neutral region as of this moment.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2934_peep_point-3-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Enon.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2934_peep_point-3-h" mid="280" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="206"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>How dare you...!<BR>You are destroying a centuries-old custom!<BR>Without the neutral zone, the Empire could sustain serious damage!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2934_peep_point-3-h" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Enon.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2934_peep_point-4" mid="281" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="207"><![CDATA[<html>$Edart's Messenger Enon$<BR>The Empire has decided to accept that damage rather than to endure an uncontrolled land infested by vermin.<BR>I regret to say that this is also the will of the Goddess...<BR>And I entreat Merca to peacefully meet the Child who will rule this land.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2934_peep_point-4" image="QN_Kali.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2934_peep_point-4-" mid="312" select_type="5" />
      <talk_question mid="208"><![CDATA[<html>$Kali$<BR>……<BR><BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Kali, hidden behind the curtain, turns and disappears.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-4" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-4-a" mid="282" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="209"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>This is a disaster!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-4-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-4-b" mid="283" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="210"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>What should we do?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-4-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-4-c" mid="284" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>What's the plan?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="211"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>...The Goddess Vestinel and the Empire have us by the throat. We can't attack this problem head-on.<BR>Captain, bring me a pen and parchment.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-4-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-4-d" mid="285" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="212"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>I will write letters to various Child lords requesting that they <FONT color=#a82424>take over Merca's territory</FONT>.<BR>I'm sure there will be a few who want Merca.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-4-d" image="QN_Kali.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-4-e" mid="286" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Could it be that one?)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="213"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Surely you don't intend to become the vassal of a Child……<BR><BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(You hear the sound of footsteps running up the Headquarters stairs.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-4-e" image="QN_Kali.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-5" mid="287" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="214"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Wait a minute, Vernicka.<BR>Someone may be coming.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-5" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-5-" mid="313" select_type="5" />
      <talk_question mid="215"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>What are you talking about? Who would come running at a time like this...</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2887_kali_merca-5" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Kali.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2887_kali_merca-5-a" mid="289" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="216"><![CDATA[<html>$Kali$<BR>……President Vernicka.<BR><BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Kali appears in front of Vernicka looking resolute.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2887_kali_merca-5-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Kali.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2887_kali_merca-5-b" mid="290" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="217"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>That face shows you know everything and aren't trying to hide it.<BR>Of course, it's even stranger that a follower of the Goddess would shout in such a loud voice.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2887_kali_merca-5-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Kali.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2887_kali_merca-5-c" mid="291" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="218"><![CDATA[<html>$Kali${sound:npc_Kali_qu9877_sp_01.ogg}<BR>I bring word from Lord Norfe.<BR>The Anti-Goddess Faction will do its utmost to help Merca.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2887_kali_merca-5-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Kali.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2887_kali_merca-5-d" mid="292" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="219"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka${sound:npc_Vernicka_9877_qu_01.ogg}<BR>There's no need.<BR>I have already requested that a Child who will offer the best conditions take over Merca.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2887_kali_merca-5-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Kali.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2887_kali_merca-5-e" mid="293" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="220"><![CDATA[<html>$Kali${sound:npc_Kali_qu9877_sp_02.ogg}<BR>Never!<BR>The fall of Merca's neutrality means the balance shifting in the Goddess' hands.<BR>Hordes of Childs will swarm Merca like a pack of wolves zeroing in on their prey.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2887_kali_merca-5-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Kali.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2887_kali_merca-5-f" mid="294" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="221"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka${sound:npc_Vernicka_9877_qu_02.ogg}<BR>Tsk... That's exactly what I want.<BR>If the various Childs fighting to get their hands on Merca can keep each other in check, it will give us some breathing room.<BR>Naturally, this is only a temporary measure to avoid the crisis directly facing us.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2887_kali_merca-5-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Kali.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2887_kali_merca-5-g" mid="295" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="222"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka${sound:npc_Vernicka_9877_qu_03.ogg}<BR>But we must escape this crisis before we can take advantage of any future opportunities.<BR>If it falls apart here and now, Merca is finished.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2887_kali_merca-5-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Kali.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2887_kali_merca-5-h" mid="296" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="223"><![CDATA[<html>$Kali${sound:npc_Kali_qu9877_sp_03.ogg}<BR>If that's what you want to do, and if Merca can escape this crisis,<BR>even opening Merca to the Childs will only leave Merca a hollowed-out shell.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2887_kali_merca-5-h" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Kali.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2887_kali_merca-5-i" mid="297" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="224"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>Is that all?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2887_kali_merca-5-i" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2887_kali_merca-5-j" mid="298" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="225"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>(You'd better be bold. She's patronizing the famed Blue Viper.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2887_kali_merca-5-j" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Kali.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2887_kali_merca-5-k" mid="299" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="226"><![CDATA[<html>$Kali${sound:npc_Kali_qu9877_sp_04.ogg}<BR>You may not trust the Anti-Goddess Faction... but the Goddess may choose to play her hand whenever she wishes.<BR>But we are your friends. We are prepared to use everything we have to guarantee Merca's safety.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2887_kali_merca-5-k" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Kali.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2887_kali_merca-5-l" mid="300" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="227"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Tsk, tsk)</FONT> <BR>It seems I raised a tiger. You certainly have a way with words.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2887_kali_merca-5-l" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Kali.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2887_kali_merca-5-m" mid="301" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="228"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>I don't know your plans,<BR>but I know the Anti-Goddess Faction's military power or technology cannot save Merca.<BR>However, the faction does know several Child lords who can serve as backup when negotiation with Hirendel fails.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2887_kali_merca-5-m" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Kali.dds" center_image="">
