         <title mid="237"><![CDATA[Visit Merca’s Headquarters]]></title>
         <contents mid="238"><![CDATA[<html>You decide to visit Vernicka to find out whether he's heard the news about Shalica. But he's got an unexpected visitor......?<BR><BR><FONT color=#086171>Merca's Heart</FONT> - <FONT color=#a82424>Vernicka</FONT></html>]]></contents>
