         <title mid="249"><![CDATA[Merca in Crisis]]></title>
         <contents mid="250"><![CDATA[<html>After hearing the message, Kali runs out urgently. You want to know what Vernicka is planning... but the girl returns before he explains.<BR><BR><FONT color=#086171>Merca's Heart</FONT> - <FONT color=#a82424>Vernicka</FONT></html>]]></contents>
         <destination mid="251"><![CDATA[Talk to Vernicka]]></destination>
         <todo_msg mid="252"><![CDATA[Talk to Vernicka.]]></todo_msg>
      </journal>
