         <title mid="253"><![CDATA[ Sincere Plea]]></title>
         <contents mid="254"><![CDATA[<html>The girl returns looking resolute and persuades Vernicka that he must allow the Anti-Goddess Faction to help him to truly protect Merca. Why is she so eager?<BR><BR><FONT color=#086171>Merca's Heart</FONT> - <FONT color=#a82424>Kali</FONT></html>]]></contents>
         <destination mid="255"><![CDATA[Listen to Kali]]></destination>
         <todo_msg mid="256"><![CDATA[Kali is back. Listen to what she has to say.]]></todo_msg>
      </journal>
